{
  "stem": "4226.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was given with, with-- three, three were picked with two Jewish guys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "One was a German engineer from Breslau, electric engineer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the other was a Greek Jewish engineer from Salonika.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the three of us, we, we were assigned in a barrack within this worker's camp which housed only electrical goods-- also belonged to the Todt Organization.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And when-- this whole setup was about a kilometer squared, maybe even less.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And our guards, which came out with us, were spread in the four corners of that square, and we were working inside.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Outside were fields, fields with potatoes, with wheat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You could see some farmhouses about a kilometer or two away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that barrack which we reassigned was an empty barrack with shelves and-- to house cables and, and stuff.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the two Germans who were in charge of that barrack only belonged to the Todt Organization, which had a different uniform from the army.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was [INAUDIBLE] with a swastika on the red armband, and on a wide strip, written Todt Organization, which was the--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--same military organization.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "T-O-D-T.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was-- the head of that was Speer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could see him two days ago on television.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was about the Reich.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was an evening-- fall of Berlin was, I think, Friday night or Saturday night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But Speer was interviewed after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the minister of, of the armament industry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was in charge of the Todt Organization in, in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But their headquarters was in Munich for, for that area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that-- no, as winter came and things got tougher, we were not given trucks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After about a month, we were walking through BMW to that place, about--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't winter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was only getting cold, October--",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
